claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table listing trade names, presentations, age indications, hemagglutinin content per dose, administration route, and mercury content for various influenza vaccines (including Flublok Quadrivalent). The table only provides formulation and administration details for Flublok and other vaccines and does not mention antigenic matching to WHO- or FDA-selected flu strains, so it does not support the claim. Note: None
